<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - OLA LSSU</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            padding: 40px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 300;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 32px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .security-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #ef4444;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .security-icon::after {
            content: 'üîí';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .otp-section {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border: 2px dashed #fca5a5;
        }

        .otp-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #dc2626;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #fca5a5;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .otp-expiry {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #b91c1c;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .instructions {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .instructions h4 {
            color: #0c4a6e;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .instructions ol {
            color: #075985;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .security-warning {
            background-color: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .security-warning h4 {
            color: #b45309;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .security-warning ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .security-warning li {
            color: #78350f;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .security-warning li::before {
            content: '‚Ä¢';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .not-you-section {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .not-you-section h4 {
            color: #b91c1c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .not-you-section p {
            color: #7f1d1d;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .otp-section {
                padding: 20px 16px;
            }

            .otp-code {
                font-size: 28px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
                padding: 12px 16px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .security-icon {
                width: 50px;
                height: 50px;
            }

            .security-icon::after {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 20px auto;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="security-icon"></div>
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Secure password reset for your account</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{ userName || 'there' }},
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                We received a request to reset the password for your OLA LSSU account.
                To proceed with resetting your password, please use the verification code provided below.
            </div>

            <!-- OTP Code Section -->
            <div class="otp-section">
                <div class="otp-label">Password Reset Code:</div>
                <div class="otp-code">{{ otp }}</div>
                <div class="otp-expiry">‚è∞ This code expires in {{ expiryMinutes || '10' }} minutes</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Instructions -->
            <div class="instructions">
                <h4>üìã How to Reset Your Password</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Return to the password reset form on our website</li>
                    <li>Enter the verification code shown above</li>
                    <li>Create a new, secure password</li>
                    <li>Confirm your new password</li>
                    <li>Save changes and log in with your new credentials</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <!-- Security Warning -->
            <div class="security-warning">
                <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Security Reminder</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Keep this code confidential - never share it with anyone</li>
                    <li>Only use this code on the official OLA LSSU website</li>
                    <li>Our team will never ask for this code via phone or email</li>
                    <li>The code expires automatically for your security</li>
                    <li>Use a strong, unique password when resetting</li>
                </ul>
            </div>



            <div class="message">
                For additional security, we recommend enabling two-factor authentication after resetting your password.
                If you need assistance, our support team is here to help.
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                Thank you for keeping your OLA LSSU account secure.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© OLA LSSU. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                This is an automated security message. For support, contact us at
                <a href="mailto:support@olalssu.com">support@olalssu.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
